Title: Specifies the use for which certain state lands are to be transferred to the city of New Rochelle
Summary: Specifies the use for which certain state lands are to be transferred to the city of New Rochelle.
LawCode: Amd §§5 & 6, Chap of 2019 (as proposed in S.6228-A & A.7846-A)
